= Locate Object =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 6  
'''Range:''' 60 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 6 rounds  
'''Area of Effect:''' 30-ft radius  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Reveals direction (but not distance) to a well-known or specifically visualized object within long range. Must be within 20 ft per level.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
